    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015140_6_4484-4509",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4484-4509",
      "markText": "沉默的人往往拥有深刻的洞察力。溪浅声喧，静水流深。",
      "totalCount": 650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015140&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4484&rangeEnd=4509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33322b0813ab6c6ag010b10?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4484&rangeEnd=4509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015140_8_3557-3601",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3557-3601",
      "markText": "受到过度刺激时，内向者的大脑甚至会直接关闭——“别再给我信息了，谢谢”——然后就黑屏了。",
      "totalCount": 611,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015140&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3557&rangeEnd=3601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33322b0813ab6c6ag010b10?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3557&rangeEnd=3601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015140_9_1432-1523",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1432-1523",
      "markText": "内向者也可以拥有社交技能，他们喜欢和人相处，享受某些类型的社交活动。但是，聚会上的寒暄会使他们的能量入不敷出。内向者更喜欢一对一的对话，团队活动可能会造成过度的刺激，耗空他们的能量。",
      "totalCount": 605,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015140&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1432&rangeEnd=1523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33322b0813ab6c6ag010b10?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1432&rangeEnd=1523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015140_6_2147-2229",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2147-2229",
      "markText": "内向和外向处于能量连续体的相反的两端，我们在连续体上的位置预示着我们获得生活能量的方式：落在连续体较内向一端的人从内在汲取能量，落在较外向一端的人则从外界汲取能量。",
      "totalCount": 598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015140&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2147&rangeEnd=2229",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33322b0813ab6c6ag010b10?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2147&rangeEnd=2229"
    },
    {
